- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the implementation of the proposed model. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are less likely but still possible as the paper deals with modeling and analyzing the dynamics of networks.
